"The user browses View 1 at the [Overview] level and learns about the overall win rates for home and away teams across venues. Next, the user selects specific venues of interest in View 1, and this interaction filters data in Views 2 and 3. In View 2 at the [Exploration] level, the user analyzes individual player performances as aggregated by venue. Concurrently, in View 3, the user explores win rate trends by venue and team type at the [Exploration] level using a heatmap. The user drills further down into individual player performance distributions in View 4 and investigates seasonal trends in match frequency at venues in View 5 at the [Detail] level."